Package: BatchMetrics
Type: Package
Title: Evaluation of batch correction
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Aleksi Laiho, Petri Toronen
Maintainer: Aleksi Laiho <aleksi.laiho@helsinki.fi>
Description: Compiles evaluation methods for batch correction models, such as 'ComBat' and 'Harman' as well as other additional batch correction methods. Includes evaluation metrics and wrapper functions for running metrics on multiple datasets. 
